"title": "6029: sin, accepting forgiveness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6029: sin, accepting forgiveness of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sinners must respond to God's offer of forgiveness through faith in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The conviction of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:20\">LAM 1:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8-John16:9\">JHN 16:8–16:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:38-1Kgs8:40\">1KI 8:38–8:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:10-Ezek33:11\">EZK 33:10–33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:29\">ACT 16:29</a></p>\n<h2>The inward response of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31\">ACT 16:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25-Acts16:34\">ACT 16:25–16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:22–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:8-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:8–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8\">EPH 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>The outward response of baptism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:4-Mark1:5\">MRK 1:4–1:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:1-Matt3:6\">MAT 3:1–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:2-Luke3:6\">LUK 3:2–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:36\">ACT 8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:11-Col2:12\">COL 2:11–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:21\">1PE 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>Confession of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:13\">PRO 28:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:20-Lev16:22\">LEV 16:20–16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:40-Lev26:42\">LEV 26:40–26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13\">2SA 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:3–32:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:40\">LAM 3:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:17-Luke15:20\">LUK 15:17–15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:18\">ACT 19:18</a></p>\n<h2>Repentance</h2>\n<h3>Turning towards God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:36-2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:36–6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:7\">ISA 55:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:21\">EZK 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:1-Matt3:2\">MAT 3:1–3:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:4\">MRK 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:2\">LUK 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:10\">2CO 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:9\">1TH 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Turning away from sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:11\">JHN 8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:3-Jer4:4\">JER 4:3–4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:1-Luke19:10\">LUK 19:1–19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:14\">JHN 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:11-Rom6:14\">ROM 6:11–6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>The making of restitution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:1-Lev6:7\">LEV 6:1–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:6-Num5:8\">NUM 5:6–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:30-Prov6:31\">PRO 6:30–6:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:12-Ezek33:16\">EZK 33:12–33:16</a></p>\n<h2>The forgiveness of others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:12\">MAT 6:12</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:14-Matt6:15\">MAT 6:14–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:25\">MRK 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></p>",
